name: Hologrammon
description:
This piece is meant to evoke in viewers a vague feeling of something familiar, and at the same time disturbing. The subconscious mind likes this kind of games, where one cannot always pinpoint right away what's so unusual about the scene before the eyes...
 
A viewer is encouraged to explore the piece, to guess what is hidden between the lines and the pixels, or right on top of them, to run through the memory in search of clues. Perhaps, one might even be successful in this venture...
